- Use modules to organize your application logically.
- Implement guards and interceptors for better security and request handling.
- Utilize DTOs (Data Transfer Objects) for validation and transformation of data.
- Leverage the built-in dependency injection system for better testability and modularity.
- Use Swagger for API documentation and ensure it is up-to-date.